OL,3,CUK inflation rises to 3.8%, driven by
OL,4,Chigh accommodation and travel costs
OL,6,F"The main driver was a hefty increase
OL,7,Fin air fares, the largest July rise
OL,8,Fsince collection of air fares changed
OL,9,Ffrom quarterly to monthly in 2001.
OL,10,FThis increase was likely due to the
OL,11,Ftiming of this year's school holidays."
OL,13,FHe added: "The price of petrol and
OL,14,Fdiesel also increased this month,
OL,15,Fcompared with a drop this time last
OL,16,Fyear. Food price inflation continues
OL,17,Fto climb, with items such as coffee,
OL,18,Ffresh orange juice, meat and chocolate
OL,19,Fseeing the biggest rises."
