OL,6,FSpeaking after the official figures
OL,7,Fwere announced, Reeves said: "We have
OL,8,Ftaken the decisions needed to
OL,9,Fstabilise the public finances, and
OL,10,Fwe're a long way from the double-digit
OL,11,Finflation we saw under the previous
OL,12,Fgovernment, but there's more to do to
OL,13,Fease the cost of living," she
OL,14,Fcontinued.
OL,16,F"That's why we've raised the minimum
OL,17,Fwage, extended the #3 bus fare cap,
OL,18,Fexpanded free school meals to over
OL,19,Fhalf a million more children and are
OL,20,Frolling out free breakfast clubs for
OL,21,Fevery child in the country.
