OL,6,FThe concerts brought in hordes of fans
OL,7,Fto arenas in Cardiff, Manchester,
OL,8,FLondon and Edinburgh, which could have
OL,9,Fdriven greater demand for hotel rooms.
OL,11,FAir fares soared by 30.2% between June
OL,12,Fand July, the biggest jump since the
OL,13,Fcollection of monthly data began in
OL,14,F2001.
OL,16,FThe average price of petrol rose by 2p
OL,17,Fper litre between June and July, and
OL,18,Fthe average diesel price by 2.9p per
OL,19,Flitre over the same period, the data
OL,20,Fshowed.
